Package: RPA
Type: Package
Title: RPA: probe reliability and differential gene expression analysis
Version: 1.7.0
Date: 2010-05-19
Author: Leo Lahti <leo.lahti@iki.fi>
Maintainer: Leo Lahti <leo.lahti@iki.fi>
Depends: R (>= 2.11.0), affy, affydata, methods
biocViews: GeneExpression, Microarray, Preprocessing, QualityControl
Description: Probabilistic analysis of probe reliability and
	     differential gene expression on short oligonucleotide
	     arrays as described in Leo Lahti et al. "Probabilistic
	     Analysis of Probe Reliability in Differential Gene
	     Expression Studies with Short Oligonucleotide Arrays",
	     TCBB/IEEE, to appear. See
	     http://doi.ieeecomputersociety.org/10.1109/TCBB.2009.38
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyLoad: yes



